highlights.text: “Lamine” by Morad is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Finland, up 18 spots at #53.
“Mun ihminen” by ELLIMEI has been on Viral Songs Finland the longest, at 115 days straight.
Katri Helena has the most spots on Viral Songs Finland. “Elämän tie” is the highest at #25.
“Charger” by TRIANGLE DES BERMUDES, MC YOSHI, Mauvais djo, and Kokosvoice is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Finland at #29.
